title: David Carbone Drum and Bass Masterclass
description:
Drum and Bass Masterclass is an unparalleled collection of pure drum and bass samples produced by one of the scenes most respected producers, Davide Carbone. 
The CD features 20 brand new drum and bass drum kits, 230+ brand new tearing breakbeat samples, 50+ speaker shaking basslines, atmospheric pads, keys, musical loops, sweeps, fx, plus 60+ brand new instrument patches pre-mapped for your favourite soft sampler

wav & rex
